---
import Section from '~/components/Section.astro';
import Nicholls from '~/assets/logos/nicholls.svg';
---

<Section id="education" eyebrow="Where I learned" title="Education" tone="base">
  <article class="mx-auto w-full max-w-5xl">
    <header
      class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6 text-center md:grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] md:items-center md:gap-8 md:text-left"
    >
      <Nicholls aria-label="Nicholls State Colonels" class="h-16 w-auto md:order-2 md:h-20 print:h-10" />
      <div class="md:order-1">
        <h3 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl">Nicholls State University</h3>
        <p class="text-accent mt-1 text-sm font-semibold md:text-base">Bachelor of Science (B.S.)</p>
        <p class="text-fg-muted mt-1 font-mono text-xs md:text-sm">August 2009 &ndash; December 2013</p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <hr class="border-glass-border my-6 border-t" />

    <ul class="text-fg-muted space-y-2 text-sm md:text-base">
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span aria-hidden="true" class="bg-accent mt-2 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full"></span>
        <span>Majored in Computer Information Systems</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span aria-hidden="true" class="bg-accent mt-2 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full"></span>
        <span>GPA: 3.6</span>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="font-display mt-10 text-lg md:text-xl">Awards</h4>
    <ul class="text-fg-muted mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm md:text-base">
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span aria-hidden="true" class="bg-accent mt-2 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full"></span>
        <span
          >Consistently awarded the President's List since the Fall 2010 semester (scholastic GPA of 3.5 or higher
          required).</span
        >
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="font-display mt-10 text-lg md:text-xl">Organizations</h4>
    <ul class="text-fg-muted mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm md:text-base">
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span aria-hidden="true" class="bg-accent mt-2 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full"></span>
        <span
          >Member of Beta Gamma Sigma, the highest recognition for a business student at an AACSB-accredited program.</span
        >
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span aria-hidden="true" class="bg-accent mt-2 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full"></span>
        <span
          >Member of Upsilon Pi Epsilon, the first international honor society in the computing and information
          disciplines.</span
        >
      </li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</Section>
